(20, '喂养知识', '2017-04-07 10:46:30', '<h5 style="margin-bottom: 5px; border: 0px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-type: none; font-size: 15px; text-align: center; font-weight: normal; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial;">Saying Goodnight to Bedtime Battles孩子晚上不愿入睡怎么办？</h5><p style="font-size: 12px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial;"><img alt="" src="http://www.noblekids.com.cn/upload/201703/23/201703231059505716.jpg" style="margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; line-height: 18px; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: middle; display: block; max-width: 100%;"></p><p style="font-size: 12px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial;">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br class="Apple-interchange-newline">Author: Charlene Lilly&nbsp;</strong></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">作者：查琳•莉莉</strong></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">In talking with parents over the last few weeks,one topic has come up time and time again, one major battle nearly every parent struggles with their child over – going to bed. Parents ask,&nbsp;<em style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">Why aren’t they tired? (I’m so tired!) Why do they want&nbsp;</em></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><em style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">to read two more books? How can I just get them to fall asleep soI can go to sleep too?&nbsp;</em>Many parents wish there was a golden answer to how they can get their child to sleep earlier, but the reality of it is that no one can make a child sleep. Children will only sleep when their body feels the natural need to rest.&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><br></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">过去几周</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">跟父母交谈，我发现大家不断地提到同一个问题，</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">几乎每个</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">家长都在为哄</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">孩子</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">睡觉而犯愁</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。父母问</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">为什么他们</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">都</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">不累</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">呢？</span>(<span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">好</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">累</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">！</span>)<span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">为什么他们</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">还</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">想</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">让我再念</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">两</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">本</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">书</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">？</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我只是</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">想</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">让他们</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">赶快入睡，然后</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我可以去睡觉</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">许多父母希望有一个</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">完美</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">答案</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，知道</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">如何让孩子早睡</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">但事实是</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">没有人可以</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">强迫</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">孩子睡觉。孩子只会</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">身体</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">感到有</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">休息</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">的自然需要时才会去睡觉</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">Don’t despair, though, dear parents! There are important things we adults can do to help build a more peaceful and natural transition into sleep-time. Perhaps the most essential step is to build a routine. For many children in the Montessori classroom, it is easy to take a nap, as naptime comes at the same time everyday – for the IC class naptime is always from 12:30 – 14:50, while for the Casa class naptime is from 1:00 to 2:30. Children thrive on routines, on knowing what is going to come next and preparing themselves for the next step. What’s more, routines often are the solution when it comes to eliminating children’s desire to test boundaries (those little things that make us adults feel so frustrated!) So when it comes to ending the bedtime battles with your little ones, perhaps the first step you should take is building a bedtime routine with them.</span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">但是不必灰心，各位</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">亲爱的</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">家长们！</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我们成年人</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">是有办法</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">帮助</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">孩子以</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">更和平自然</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">的方式</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">过渡到睡眠时间</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">的</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。最关键的是</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">要</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">建立</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">起日常惯例</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。蒙特梭利教室</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">里的孩子每天都会午休，时间固定</span><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">——IC</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">班</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在</span><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">12:30 - 14:50</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">而</span><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">Casa</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">班在</span><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">1:00 - 2:30</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">孩子的成长有赖于日常惯例，依赖于</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">知道接下来</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">要做</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">什么</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">并</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">为下一步作准备。更重要的是</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，在打消</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">孩子测试边界</span><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">(test boundaries)</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">的欲望时，日常惯例</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">通常</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">是</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">解决方案</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">所以</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果想要在睡前战争中获胜，</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">也许你应该采取的第一步</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">就是跟孩子建立</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">一个睡前常规。</span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><img alt="" src="http://www.noblekids.com.cn/upload/201703/23/201703231100183380.jpg" style="margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; line-height: 18px; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, 宋体; font-size: 12px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: middle; display: block; max-width: 100%;"></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">Making Your Own Bedtime Routine</strong></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">和孩子一起建立睡前常规</span></strong></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">It can be helpful for many parents to create a bedtime routine chart, which acts as a visual aid for the child to help them remember what they should do before they go to bed. As the routine is one parents engage in together with their child, it is essential that parents take time to brainstorm what activities are considered acceptable as part of the bedtime rituals. Once you have decided what to do each night, you can take pictures of the child doing that activity and paste them on the chart – children love to see pictures of themselves! You can also have them drawpictures of themselves doing the task. The important thing is to incorporate the child in the design of this chart, so that they become interested in referring to and relying on it.&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><br></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">创建睡前常规图表</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">会很有帮助，作为</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">视觉</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">指导，它可以</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">帮助</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">孩子</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">记住他们</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">睡前</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">应该做什么。常规是父母和孩子一起参与的</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">父母</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">需要</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">花时间头脑风暴</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">来确定什么样的活动</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">可</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">被</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">接受的睡前仪式的一部分。一旦决定</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">了每晚</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">要做什么</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">你可以</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">拍下</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">孩子做活动的照片</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">并把照片</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">粘贴在图表</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">上。</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">孩子们喜欢看到自己的照片</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">你也可以让他们画自己</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在做任务时的照片</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">要配合</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">孩子</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">来设计</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这个图表</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，让</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他们</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">对此产生</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">兴趣</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">并形成依赖</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span></p><span style="font-size: 12px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><img alt="" src="http://www.noblekids.com.cn/upload/201703/23/201703231234173417.jpg" style="margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; line-height: 18px; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, 宋体; font-size: 12px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: middle; display: block; max-width: 100%;"><br class="Apple-interchange-newline" style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 12px;"><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">What Should We Do Before Bed?</strong></p><p style="font-size: 16px; word-break: normal; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-